00:16:20,599 --> 00:16:22,701
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita berhenti tinggal bersama seperti pasangan.</font>

187
00:16:23,736 --> 00:16:25,571
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan tinggallah bersama Jung Won.</font>

188
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:28,807
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau...</font>

189
00:16:30,809 --> 00:16:31,944
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau...</font>

190
00:16:32,378 --> 00:16:33,646
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mendengar semuanya dari Jung Won.</font>

191
00:16:33,646 --> 00:16:36,782
<font color=#FFFF00>Mata Jin Joo sekarang sedang bengkak,
