192
00:16:45,090 --> 00:16:46,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, terima kasih.</font>

193
00:16:50,729 --> 00:16:52,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergilah. Aku harus berangkat kerja sekarang.</font>

194
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:56,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, cepat bersiaplah.</font>

195
00:17:06,078 --> 00:17:08,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, apa ini semua?</font>

196
00:17:08,781 --> 00:17:10,015
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ditendang keluar.</font>

197
00:17:14,553 --> 00:17:16,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, sikat gigimu ketinggalan.</font>

198
00:17:19,091 --> 00:17:20,426
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi?</font>

199
00:17:20,492 --> 00:17:23,796
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin pacaran dengan Jin Joo
