200
00:17:24,530 --> 00:17:25,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Ho Bang.</font>

201
00:17:26,432 --> 00:17:28,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sibuk. Pergi dulu.</font>

202
00:17:43,549 --> 00:17:45,417
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kenapa masak sup tahu?</font>

203
