204
00:17:51,690 --> 00:17:53,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, hentikan.</font>

205
00:17:56,929 --> 00:17:58,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Cobalah.</font>

206
00:17:59,798 --> 00:18:02,134
<font color=#FFFF00>- Enak sekali.
- Enak, bukan? Makanlah.</font>

207
00:18:02,368 --> 00:18:03,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini.</font>

208
00:18:05,337 --> 00:18:06,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Lahap juga makanmu.</font>

209
00:18:07,206 --> 00:18:08,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Aah.</font>

210
00:18:25,891 --> 00:18:27,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana menurutmu?</font>

211
00:18:39,338 --> 00:18:40,472
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa ini terlihat bagus.</font>

212
00:18:40,472 --> 00:18:41,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah. Aku akan memakai ini.</font>

213
00:18:46,645 --> 00:18:48,547
<font color=#FFFF00>Semoga sukses di perusahaan penerbitan.</font>

214
00:18:50,516 --> 00:18:52,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku agak gugup hari ini.</font>

215
00:18:52,618 --> 00:18:54,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kau berusaha...,</font>

216
00:18:54,420 --> 00:18:56,789
