301
00:24:43,835 --> 00:24:45,537
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan mereka bisa membawa Gong Joo dari pusat.</font>

302
00:24:45,837 --> 00:24:49,474
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku merasa Hae Sung ada di sini
