303
00:24:51,209 --> 00:24:52,277
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

304
00:24:56,915 --> 00:24:58,483
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hae Sung.
- Hyung.</font>

305
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:03,054
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kalian bisa masuk bersama?</font>

306
00:25:03,088 --> 00:25:05,624
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kami bertemu di depan restoran.
