307
00:25:10,929 --> 00:25:12,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Sung.</font>

308
00:25:13,532 --> 00:25:14,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Sertifikat pendaftaran usaha kita.</font>

309
00:25:17,102 --> 00:25:19,704
<font color=#FFFF00>"Pemilik bisnis, Sung Hae Chul."
