314
00:25:31,316 --> 00:25:32,417
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar juga.</font>

315
00:25:32,784 --> 00:25:35,387
<font color=#FFFF00>Tinggal bersama Gong Joo, hyung...</font>

316
00:25:35,620 --> 00:25:39,691
<font color=#FFFF00>...Young In, dan Soo Ji,
