318
00:25:42,928 --> 00:25:43,962
<font color=#FFFF00>Bolehkah?</font>

319
00:25:47,199 --> 00:25:48,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih, Hyung.</font>

320
00:25:49,100 --> 00:25:50,502
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo kita bekerja keras dan menghasilkan banyak uang!</font>

321
00:25:50,502 --> 00:25:53,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat kita punya banyak uang,
