328
00:26:14,159 --> 00:26:16,261
<font color=#FFFF00>- Semangat!
- Semangat!</font>

329
00:26:21,333 --> 00:26:22,701
<font color=#FFFF00>Sung Hae Chul, kau perlu mempelajari resepnya.</font>

330
00:26:23,001 --> 00:26:24,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa? 'Kan ada kau.</font>

331
00:26:24,970 --> 00:26:26,304
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bertugas mengelola gedung.</font>

332
00:26:27,105 --> 00:26:28,974
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila aku tidak di sini,
