370
00:29:10,568 --> 00:29:11,703
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ini sungguh manusia?</font>

371
00:29:12,037 --> 00:29:13,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau bisa sekejam itu?</font>

372
00:29:14,506 --> 00:29:16,274
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku memberimu pelajaran
