373
00:29:16,408 --> 00:29:17,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepas!</font>

374
00:29:17,909 --> 00:29:19,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepas! Lepaskan aku!</font>

375
00:29:19,844 --> 00:29:22,947
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei! Aku tidak akan membiarkanmu. Mengerti?</font>

376
00:29:23,581 --> 00:29:24,682
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan aku!</font>

377
00:29:24,682 --> 00:29:25,984
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan seperti ini di rumah sakit.</font>

378
00:29:35,527 --> 00:29:37,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, Jung Won. Hae Sung!</font>

379
00:29:40,598 --> 00:29:41,699
<font color=#FFFF00>Ho Bang.</font>

380
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,234
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

381
00:29:43,234 --> 00:29:45,904
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku melacak kartu kredit Park Dong Seok...</font>

382
00:29:45,904 --> 00:29:47,272
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menemukan hotel tempat dia menginap.</font>

383
00:29:47,338 --> 00:29:50,542
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aku akan ke sana sekarang.
